\begin_layout Standard
这个文献所使用的记号：在光锥坐标系下，对于任何四速度–
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
v^{\pm}=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left(v^{0}\pm v^{3}\right),\quad v^{\perp}=\left(v^{1},v^{2}\right).
\]

\end_inset

通常使用两个特殊的类光矢量，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
n_{+}=\left(1,0,0,1\right)/\sqrt{2}, &  & n^{+}=\left(1,0,0,-1\right)/\sqrt{2}\\
n_{-}=\left(1,0,0,-1\right)/\sqrt{2} &  & n^{-}=\left(1,0,0,1\right)/\sqrt{2}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

